author: @sweetserendipity1402
text:
tbh i don't think i could ever write it in words of how i feel about jaehyun. he continues to surprise me in everything he do, and he's so passionate about music and i couldn't be more in love with him. also no words could describe how much i love his voice, i felt like i fell in love all over again everytime i hear his voice. i'm so so proud of you, jaehyun! and i can't wait for more of you in the future.

also, weird thing is that for the past few weeks whenever i see jaehyun, a certain song came to my mind, Carole King's 'Anyone at All'. i think maybe because the song perfectly describe how comfortable i felt whenever i see him. i just hope that our valentine boy remember that he will always have us who will love him the way that he is. if ypu never heard of the song, go and listen to it. i might also think of that song because i was thinking how jae's voice could fit this song too.

anyway, i love you my peach, my valentine, can't wait for more 🧡

author: @wanttobeloved
text:
First of All,

To Mr.JUNG and Mrs.JUNG,
Jaehyun's Bumeonim

This is one of million fangirls of Jaehyun,
Mrs.JUNG, thank you so much for giving birth to Jaehyunie, for breastfeeding baby Jaehyun the best nutrition, for giving so much love to Jaehyunie, for giving your life just to make Jaehyunie born this awesome, thank you for everything that Mrs.JUNG taught Jaehyunie how to play piano when he was young and about fashion💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚
Mr.JUNG, thank you so much for teaching little Jaehyun the basic lessons of life, for giving advices to Jaehyun, for giving the best genes and visuals to Jaehyunie💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚

To Jaehyun's Halmeonim and Harabeoji,
Thank you so much for taking care of Jaehyunie, and for giving the best advices about life to Jaehyunie💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚


And, to Jaehyunie,
Thank you so much for bringing me to your 22 Brothers in NCT💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚
I'm not the best, the smartest, the prettiest, the sexiest nor the richest fangirl of yours, but thank you so much for letting me to grow older with you💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚
These 8 years, 10 months and 22 days, from the day you were introduced as one of SMRookie Boys
I didnt think that i could survive with you for this long time, thank you for 'saving' me from suicidal attempts, Jaehyun💚
You know what? I'll never get bored for talking about you to my Grandparents, in the cemetery, but i couldnt visit my Grandparents at any moment like what i did before, so i'll do visit my Grandparents in every Friday, it's the day you were born, and i just wanted to make my Grandparents know that a man named Jung Yuno is one of the best parts in my life

I'm sorry that i couldnt be able to following the contents of NCT, like every day, i had to focus on my study and i had to focus on my residency
But, i'm gonna do my best to vote NCT (127, DREAMies and/or WayV) anytime it's needed to do

Take care of yourself, Jaehyunie💚
Whenever you need someone to talk to, we're able on bubble, ig and twitter
I hope you'll take care of your mental health, physical health, your penile health, your hair health and take care of your peace of mind, Jaehyunie💚


I added this cover to my playlist, you sound so heaven touchㅠㅠㅠㅠㅠㅠㅠㅠㅠㅠ




And, deep condolences for the victims of Itaewon Halloween Tragedy on October 29th, 2022
May Almighty God give them the most peaceful rests and the most beautiful places in Heaven💚
We hope their families are strong for letting the deceased victims rest in peace💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚💚




Stay safe and stay healthy, everyone💚
Almighty God bless you

재현아 이렇게 깜짝 선물을 주다니 정말 고마워. 나에겐 늘 언제나 선물 같은 재현이지만 올해 재현이가 보여주는 모습들은 나도 그렇고 재프들의 마음을 유독 울리는지... 아마 재현이가 어떤 마음인지 알기에 그러는 거 아닐까 싶어. 우리 시간을 함께라며 이젠 정말 공유 받고 서로를 아는 사이가 되기도 하고, 재현이가 올초에 말했던 것처럼 결과만이 아니라 과정들을 보여준다고 했던 말처럼 그 과정들을 알기에 재현이의 마음도 재현이가 보여주는 것들이 더 마음에 남는듯해. 포레버 온리부터 이번 커버곡까지 팬들이 노래하는 재현이 좋아하는 거 알고 준비해주는 마음이 얼마나 예쁘고 고마운지... 심지어 재프들이 응원하고 좋아하는 재현이의 모습을 재현이도 행복하다하고 즐기는 게 눈에 보여서 얼마나 사랑스럽고 행복한지 몰라.
재현아 늘 충분히 잘하고 있고 진심으로 자랑스러워하고 좋아하며 응원하는 너의 편들이 있으니 재현이의 노래 작업들이 더 즐거웠으면 좋겠다. 재현이의 따스하고 예쁜 노래 선물 정말 고마워. 덕분에 올가을겨울을 날 수 있는 에너지가 생겼어ᖰ(｡◠‿◠｡)ᖳ

author: @EmilyTan
text:
Jaehyun is always looking for ways to give back to his fans and always showing how appreciative he is! Despite being busy preparing for the 2 Baddies comeback as well as releasing Forever Only, he still made time to prepare this for his fans after hearing people wanted more covers from fansign events and you can tell how passionate he is about music.

He has always expressed on bubble or in his ments and interviews that he feels like he has received so much love and wants to repay that in different ways, and rather than necessarily saying things directly, wishes to show things through his actions. This cover truly encompasses all of that and what an amazing cover that suits Jaehyun so well and his vocals are shining as always!!!

author: @lifeispuckfuck
text:
To. 재현이에게💚
재현님~ 우선 지금 너무 행복해서 고맙다는 말로 시작을 할게요. 어제 저녁에 버블로 이어폰 챙기라는 버블을 받고 받은 그 순간부터 오늘 오후 6시까지 계속 설레는 마음으로 기다렸어요. 재현이가 이어폰을 챙기라고 한거면 음악을 준비했다는건데, 요즘 "질주" 활동으로 많이 바빴을 텐데 재현이는 그 바쁜 와중에도 또 선물을 준비했구나 하고 너무 행복하기도 하고 감사했어요💚
앞으로도 재현이의 무궁무진한 음악 생활을 응원하고 또 응원할게요💚
항상 좋은 음악으로 시즈니들에게 선물을 주어서 고마워요. 이번 크리스마스엔 재현이의 이 음악으러 따듯하고 안정감 있는 크리스마스를 더 특별한 날로 시작해서 보낼 수 있을 것 같아요, 무엇보다 이 노래가 지금 이 시기에 듣기 너무 좋은 노래라 재현이의 노래를 낸 시기가 너무 최고라고 생각이 들어요!글을 너무 급하게 쓰느라 두서가 없었지만 결국 요약하면 정재현 너가 최고라는거 !! 앞으로도 좋은 노래 많이 해주세요! 우리 시즈니들은 항상 뒤에서 지켜보며 응원할게요💚
